transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello. Ji good afternoon, good evening sir. Navzar baat kar raha hu sir India Mart se, kaise hain sir aap?
Executive: Mai theek hu batao.
Customer: Ji ji mai sir wahi kal jo aapko bataya tha to aapne call back karne ke liye bola tha. Ek to cheez ye hai sir ki.
Executive: Ji.
Executive: Mai travel kar raha hu mai kal pahuchunga office to kal phone karna.
Executive: Achcha to kal kitne baje karu?
Customer: Kal karo tum dopahar me 2 baje, kam se kam meri meeting rahegi 2 baje.
Executive: 2 se 3 to sir hamara wo rehta hai lunch to usse pehle kar le 1 baje.
Customer: 3 baje kar lena.
Executive: 3 baje okay, theek hai 3 baje.
Executive: Theek hai okay, thank you.
